Restaurant Order Calculator Prototype

This is the Step 2 Prototype for my CIS 2085 Java Final Project.
The prototype demonstrates:

Menu stored using arrays

Ordering loop with validation

Quantity collection

Subtotal calculation using a method

Basic formatted order summary

This version does not yet include tax, discount, or tip.
Those will be added in Step 3 (Final Implementation).

How to Run

Open in NetBeans → Run Project
Requires Java 8+.

